	<Text>The Crimea Shield was awarded to those engaged in the battles of the Crimea as well as to civilians. The award criteria are:
- to have been engaged in one major operation at the Crimea
- to have served at the Crimea during first or second battle for Crimea for 60 days
- to have been wounded while serving on the Crimea</Text>
